analysis_commentary: The proportion of patients dying in their usual place of residence has risen steadily over the course of the time period; increasing from 37.9% of deaths between January and December 2008, to 43.9% of deaths between April 2012 and March 2013.
data_source: National end of life care intelligence network, End of life care profiles
